Dotfiles to setup a bash environment.
This directory needs to be in $HOME/dotfiles

cd
mkdir ~/dotfiles
git clone git://github.com/robersom/dotfiles.git dotfiles

to install, run . ~/dotfiles/install.sh

or in bash:

ln -s dotfiles/bash_profile .bash_aliases
ln -s dotfiles/gemrc .gemrc
ln -s dotfiles/irbrc .irbrc
ln -s dotfiles/gitignore .gitignore

mkdir ~/bin
ln -s dotfiles/git-publish-branch bin/
